你能够调用以下的API:
[['EnergyInvestment.find_articles', {'name': 'EnergyInvestment.find_articles', 'description': 'This function searches for articles on a specific topic and year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the articles, e.g., retirement energy investment.'}, {'name': 'year', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The year of the articles.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of up to five matching articles, each with a title, summary, and link.'}]}], ['EnergyInvestment.get_historical_data', {'name': 'EnergyInvestment.get_historical_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical data for specified energy companies for a given year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'year', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The year for which historical data is requested.'}, {'name': 'companies', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of company names.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Historical data for the specified companies, including stock prices and financial performance.'}]}], ['EnergyInvestment.get_real_time_data', {'name': 'EnergyInvestment.get_real_time_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves real-time market data for specified energy companies.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companies', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of company names.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Real-time market data for the specified companies, including current stock prices and trading volumes.'}]}], ['EnergyInvestment.get_investment_advice', {'name': 'EnergyInvestment.get_investment_advice', 'description': 'This function provides investment advice based on company names.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyNames', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of company names.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'Investment advice for the specified companies, including potential risks and benefits.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `EnergyInvestment.find_articles` 并传入 `topic` 和 `year`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "EnergyInvestment.find_articles",
    "args": "{'topic': 'retirement energy investment', 'year': 2023}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
